Overview Open Science practices can boost your enjoyment and productivity when working on empirical research projects. Yet, imagine not only you, but also other members of your department and school to use similar tools and methods to collaborate?
Luckily, you don&rsquo;t have to reinvent the wheel and can follow best-practices of leading research groups.
Experiences in transitioning to open science   Lowndes et al. 2019, &ldquo;Supercharge your research - a ten-week plan for open data science&rdquo;
